  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/258c52225dcba7cca3e0de09bbd88189.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/258c52225dcba7cca3e0de09bbd88189.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.poster.avif?t=1748708196\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.webm?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.mp4?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/f1c25268f02015ff02f83c08f31c6422.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/f1c25268f02015ff02f83c08f31c6422.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Primal Hunger</strong> is a battle royale unlike any other. You begin your hunt as a fledgling creature fighting for survival and hunting prey to evolve. Climb up the evolutionary chain to become a <strong>Final Evolution</strong> and eliminate your foes. The last player standing is the <strong>Alpha Predator!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/bbf21be71956048e3b230ccbc39725e0.poster.avif?t=1748708196\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/bbf21be71956048e3b230ccbc39725e0.webm?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/bbf21be71956048e3b230ccbc39725e0.mp4?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/72de46e12e0873d212ff48ee220395ba.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/72de46e12e0873d212ff48ee220395ba.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=57 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each kill you gain <strong>Catalyst</strong>, the island's resource. Different types of catalyst determine your evolutionary path on your way to becoming a <strong>Final Evolution</strong>. Each provides different playstyles so choose your hunting grounds wisely. There are countless creatures to evolve into, so no two matches will be alike. You'll constantly find yourself playing as and hunting against new evolutions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/37fd365f8ac79e6e67594a9caf4aa19e.poster.avif?t=1748708196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/37fd365f8ac79e6e67594a9caf4aa19e.webm?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/37fd365f8ac79e6e67594a9caf4aa19e.mp4?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/02ad5a3a56ea9f5f39e8fc4cde87ed7a.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/02ad5a3a56ea9f5f39e8fc4cde87ed7a.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike other Battle Royales, death does not immediately spell the end.  Your evolutionary <strong>Catalyst</strong> can sustain you to continue your hunt, but beware! There is not enough <strong>Catalyst</strong> on the island to support more than one <strong>Final Evolution</strong>, so death will become permanent when one emerges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/b8dffa2ef941f4f7bd4027acf37fab86.poster.avif?t=1748708196\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/b8dffa2ef941f4f7bd4027acf37fab86.webm?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/b8dffa2ef941f4f7bd4027acf37fab86.mp4?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/258c52225dcba7cca3e0de09bbd88189.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/258c52225dcba7cca3e0de09bbd88189.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.poster.avif?t=1748708196\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.webm?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/58233f1df03b77107d8c2a49e58137c1.mp4?t=1748708196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras/f1c25268f02015ff02f83c08f31c6422.avif?t=1748708196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702610/extras_big/f1c25268f02015ff02f83c08f31c6422.avif?t=1748708196 width=800 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Primal Hunger</strong> is a battle royale unlike any other. You begin your hunt as a fledgling creature fighting for survival and hunting prey to evolve. Climb up the evolutionary chain to become a <strong>Final Evolution</strong> and eliminate your foes. The last player standing is the <strong>Alpha Predator!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a